  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In a equivalence analysis, we determined whether IL-6 can be assessed using a new
      densitometric point-of-care (POC) assay (turn-around -time: 20 minutes).IL-6 measurements
      were compared to test results obtained with conventional ELISA analysis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In an equivalence analysis, we determined whether IL-6 can be assessed using a new
      densitometric point-of-care (POC) assay (turn-around -time: 20 minutes) that allows IL-6
      measurements at the bedside. We then compared the respective test results to those obtained
      with conventional ELISA analysis
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
